### Fetchling Abilities
***Ability Score Increase.*** Your Dexterity score increases by 2, and your Charisma score increases by 1.

***Creature Type.*** You are a Humanoid.

***Size.*** You are Medium.

***Speed.*** Your walking speed is 30 feet.

***Superior Darkvision.*** You can see in dim light within 120 feet of you as if it were bright light and in darkness as if it were dim light. You discern colors in that darkness only as shades of gray.

***Stealthy.*** You have proficiency in Stealth.

***??.*** Advantage on seeing through shadows and illusions.

***Shadow Blending.*** While in dim light and shadows, you are considered heavily obscured instead of lightly obscured.

***Light Sensitivity.*** You have disadvantage on Wisdom (Perception) checks that rely on sight when trying to perceive something in an area of bright light.

\columnbreak

