\pagebreak

### Clever Shadow
You can use your shadow to manipulate objects.
You can store objects in your shadow.
You can use your shadow to temporarily create objects (permanent hp loss until item is returned).

### Shadow Walker
You learn to walk along the edges of the boundary of the Shadow Plane. You gain the following benefits, based on your level:
- **9th level:** You can cast the *shadow walk* spell (self only) and regain the ability to do so when you finish a long rest.
- **13th level:** You can bring along passengers when you cast the *shadow walk* spell. You can also cast *plane shift* (self only), moving between the Material Plane and Shadow Plane, up to twice every seven days.
- **17th level:** You can bring along passengers when you cast the *plane shift* spell.
